msgid ""
"[skull]: -X. X is half the amount of doom on enemies and assets in play, rounded down (to a max of 4)."
"[cultist]: -1. If there is a [[Cultist]] enemy at your location, reveal another token."
"[tablet]: -3. If you fail, place 1 doom on an enemy at your location with no doom on it."
"[elder_thing]: -4. If you fail, take 1 damage or 1 horror."
msgstr ""
"[skull]：–X。X为场上敌人和支援上毁灭标记总数的一半，向下取整（最多为4）。"
"[cultist]：–1。如果你所在地点有[[异教徒]]敌人，再揭示一个混乱标记。"
"[tablet]：–3。如果你检定失败，在你所在地点一个没有毁灭标记的敌人上放置1个毁灭标记。"
"[elder_thing]：–4。如果你检定失败，受到1点伤害或1点恐惧。"

msgid ""
"[skull]: -X. X is the amount of doom on enemies and assets in play (to a max of 8)."
"[cultist]: -3. If there is a [[Cultist]] enemy at your location, reveal another token."
"[tablet]: -5. If you fail, place 1 doom on an enemy at your location (with no doom on it, if able)."
"[elder_thing]: -6. If you fail, take 1 damage or 1 horror."
msgstr ""
"[skull]：–X。X为场上敌人和支援上毁灭标记的总数（最多为8）。"
"[cultist]：–3。如果你所在地点有[[异教徒]]敌人，再揭示一个混乱标记。"
"[tablet]：–5。如果你检定失败，在你所在地点一个敌人上放置1个毁灭标记（如可能，放置在没有毁灭标记的敌人上）。"
"[elder_thing]：–6。如果你检定失败，受到1点伤害或1点恐惧。"

msgid "Errata: During this scenario, putting locations into play counts as meeting the 'reveal' reaction condition on the No Place Like Home task card."
msgstr "勘误：在此剧情中，将地点置入游戏区域视为满足 “吾家可归” 任务卡牌上 “揭示” 的触发条件。"

msgid "Remove the Maria Rivera story asset from the game."
msgstr "将玛莉亚·里维拉剧情支援从游戏中移除。"

msgid "If Ursula Downs was chosen as an investigator:"
msgstr "如果你以厄休拉·唐斯进行游戏："

msgid "You and your assistant Jake each chime in with a few details of your own as Andy recounts the story that brought you together. You suppress a shudder as you recall the horrors you witnessed in the Amazon, and the incident that took Jake’s leg."
msgstr "安迪回忆是什么让你们相逢的时候，你和你的助手杰克也都补充了一点自己的细节。你回想起亚马逊森林里见证的恐怖，还有让杰克失去一条腿的事故，不由得打了个寒战。"

msgid "The dank tunnels beneath R’lyeh branch and thread endlessly like the capillaries of some giant beast. Shining nodules are stationed at intervals in the walls, pulsing with soft light. After making camp on the third evening, you sit across the tunnel from Andy as he scribbles furiously in his notebook. The conversation soon turns to the events that led you both into Tillinghast’s employ."
msgstr "拉莱耶底下的黑暗隧道错综复杂，延伸无尽，仿佛某只巨兽的毛细血管。墙壁之间生长的瘤结脉动着柔光。第三夜扎营后，你在隧道里坐在了安迪旁边，而他正疯狂地在笔记本上涂写着什么。对话很快就转向了你俩为什么受雇于蒂林哈斯特。"

msgid ""
"“The long and short of it is… Mr. Tillinghast said he had another big story for me. A chance for me to make my big break. And, well, maybe enough money to pay off my tab at Hibb’s.” He looks bashful. “I had to let off some steam after my last gig! A lot of steam.”"
"A tremor rocks the tunnels. Andy’s face grows ashen as he leans in. “I have a theory. This city? It’s rising. I mean, <i>still</i> rising. The shakes, the crumbling foundation, the fact that it was underwater before and now it isn’t. You saw the ship graveyard in the city spires, right? Ships’ve been going missing in this stretch of ocean for centuries. I don’t know what’s causing it, but I keep having these dreams…”"
"The next day, you discover a vast cavern. The walls and ceiling are honeycombed with small round holes that branch off haphazardly into a labyrinthe warren. Andy rushes to the entrance of one particularly foul-smelling tunnel and picks up a bloody scrap of cloth. “I don’t know what lives here, but I think they like eating people.”"
"Further in, fleshy, bilious growths line the tunnel, oozing a thick, phlegmy ichor. Could anyone actually be left alive down here?"
msgstr ""
"“长话短说……蒂林哈斯特先生说他有一篇大报道可以给我，让我名声大噪。还有，唔，足够付清我在希伯特的账单。”他看若有些害羞，“上一份工作之后，我得发泄一下!不过发泄得有点多了。”"
"隧道里一阵震颤。安迪前倾一步，脸色煞白：“我有个想法。这座城?它在升起，我是说，还在升起。这些震动、崩塌的地基，它之前还在水下，现在已经不是了。你看到城市尖塔的沉船坟场了吧?几个世纪以来，船只经过这片海域就会失踪。我不知道原因，但我一直梦到……""
"第二天，你们发现了一个巨大的洞穴。岩壁和天顶都遍布小圆洞，排布杂乱，状若迷宫。安迪冲到一条恶臭的隧道入口处，捡起一块染血的破布。“我不知道这里有什么生物，但我想它们是吃人的。”"
"再往里走，隧道里都是恶心的肉质增生，渗出粘稠的脓液。里面真有人能生还吗?"

msgid ""
"The tunnels beyond the heart of the city slope ever-downward through a series of complexes: ancient alien factories frozen in time. “I wonder what they made here,” Ruby says. Clawed metal appendages hang over mile-long tracks while gargantuan statues stare down from high alcoves. Rather than walk in the eerie silence, you ask your companions what brought them into Tillinghast’s employ."
"“Truth is, Tillinghast caught me trying to sneak off with some of his, er, stock,” Ruby says. “Not my best work. But that man knows how to spin any deal in his favor. He offered me a job, instead. The money was good⸺better than the stuff I’d nabbed⸺so I said yes. I’ve been saving up for retirement for a while now.”"
"The factories give way to a labyrinthine tunnel system. After days of exploration, you discover a vast cavern. The walls and ceiling are honeycombed with small round holes that branch off haphazardly into a labyrinthine warren. The gory remains of a young man in a patchwork cloak lies prone in front of one tunnel. The stench is unbearable."
"“This is the same kind of cloak the other fella was wearing,” Ruby holds a handkerchief to her mouth as she pulls a small scrap of paper out of the man’s pocket. Scrawled in blood are two words: SEND HELP. You look down the tunnel. Fleshy, bilious growths line the sides, giving it the look of a giant esophagus. A far worse stench emanates from within."
"“Something tells me there’s nobody left to help. Still, there could be something worthwhile down there,” Ruby says, the usual panache noticeably absent from her voice."
msgstr ""
"城市中心底下的隧道深入之后更加复杂：仿佛是远古的工厂，冻结在了时间之中。“我好奇这里造过什么。”露比说道。几里长的轨道上吊着带爪的金属附肢，高处的壁龛里有庞大的雕像在俯视。你不想在前进的时候陷入诡异的沉默，于是问起同伴，到底是怎么才会给蒂林哈斯特打工的。"
"“真相是，蒂林哈斯特趁我在偷他的，呃，库存的时候，把我抓了个正着。”露比说道，“对我来说算不上光彩。但这个人懂得把任何事情都变得对自己有利。他转而给了我一份活。钱不少—比我要拿的东西都多—所以我接受了。打那起我就在攒钱准备退休了。”"
"工厂变成了错综复杂的隧道网络。几天的探索之后，你们发现了一个巨大的洞穴。岩壁和天顶都遍布小圆洞，排布杂乱，状若迷宫。其中一条隧道前面俯躺着一个男子，他血淋淋的尸体上穿着补丁长袍。恶臭叫人难以忍受。"
"“这袍子和另一个家伙穿的一样。”露比用手帕捂着嘴，一边从男子的口袋里掏出一小张纸，上面用血潦草地写着两个字：求援。你向隧道远处望去。两边都是恶心的肉质增生，让里面看着就像个巨大的食道。远处散发的腐臭更是叫人恶心得多。"
"“我有种感觉，里面已经没人要救了。不过，可能还是有些东西值得进去一探。”露比说道，声音里已经没有了往常的潇洒。"

msgid "If an investigator has the \"Walk in Faith\" task:"
msgstr "如果调查员有“追随信仰”任务:"

msgid "Task: Walking in Faith"
msgstr "任务：追随信仰"

msgid "An overwhelming sense of dread and awe fills your chest as you stare at the honeycomb of spongy, fleshy tunnels and the littered debris on the ground. There are several torn cloaks and a broken lantern. A massive chalk arcle composed of Latinate words and eldritch symbols has been drawn in the center of the room. A ritual of protection, perhaps? More disturbigly, a sacred symbol of your own faith is inscribed in its center. Were the ones who drew it fellow adherents of your faith? They could be heretics, but as you think about it, you wonder if they were drawn, much like you, to this ancient city by fate. As you descend into the belly of the beast, your stomach aches. Has your faith led you astray?"
msgstr "你凝视着蜂窝一样遍布孔洞的血肉隧道和地上散落的碎渣，内心的恐惧和敬畏几乎将你压垮。还有几件撕碎的长袍和摔坏的提灯。洞室中央有一个粉笔画成的大圆，写着拉丁文，绘有骇人的符号。也许是个保护的结界?最叫人不安的是，圆阵中心刻绘了你所信仰的神圣符号。画出它的人是你的教友吗?他们可能是异教徒，但你一加思量，就想知道他们是不是也和你一样，是被命运引来了这座古城。你深入巨曾腹中，肚子痛了起来。你的信仰是否已经领你误入歧途?"

msgid "<i>\"I have such doubts.\"</i>"
msgstr "<i>“我有疑问。”</i>"

msgid "Erase 1 progress under \"Walk in Faith\" in your Campaign Log. The first time each investigator would draw from the encounter deck in the next scenario, they may draw 1 card from their deck instead."
msgstr "在剧本日志中，“追随信仰”下擦去1进展。每位调查员下场冒险第一次将要从遭遇牌库抽取时，可以改为从自己牌库抽取1张卡牌。"

msgid "<i>\"I am firm in my resolve.\"</i>"
msgstr "<i>“我坚定不移。”</i>"

msgid "Mark 2 progress under \"Walk in Faith\" in your Campaign Log and suffer 1 mental trauma. The first time each investigator draws an encounter card in the next scenario, that encounter card gains surge."
msgstr "在剧本日志中，“追随信仰”下记录2进展并承受1点精神创伤。每位调查员下场冒险第一次抽取遭遇卡牌时，该遭遇卡牌获得涌动。"

msgid "When gathering the <i>Star Spawn</i> encounter set, only gather the Infected Star Spawn enemy, Remove each other card in that set from the game."
msgstr "在收齐<i>星之眷族</i>遭遇组时，只收齐感染的星之眷族敌人。将该遭遇组的其他所有卡牌从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Put Apiary Entrance into play, <i>(Beckoning Light)</i> side faceup."
msgstr "将养育场入口放置入场，<i>（引诱之光）</i>面朝上。"

msgid "Each investigator begins play at Apiary Entrance."
msgstr "每位调查员从养育场入口开始游戏。"

msgid "Build the act deck using act 1a-\"Unsettling Signs\" and act 2a-\"Lost Pilgrims.\" Remove the other act from the game."
msgstr "使用场景1a“不安的兆象”和场景2a“失落的朝圣者”创建场景牌库。将其余场景从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Build the act deck using act 1a—\"Unsettling Signs\" and act 2a—\"The Hive Mind.\" Remove the other act from the game."
msgstr "使用场景1a“不安的兆象”和场景2a“蜂巢思维”创建场景牌库。将其余场景从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Remove the Mother enemy from the game."
msgstr "将主母敌人从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Set each of the following aside, out of play: each [[Apiary]] location, the Grotesque Amalgam and the double-sided Squamous Parasite [tdc_rune_t] enemies, the Maria Rivera, Ancient Relic [tdc_rune_s], and Grisly \"Mask\" story assets, the <i>Pilgrims</i> and <i>The Inescapable</i> encounter sets, and each copy of the Parasitic Transformation weakness."
msgstr "将以下卡牌放在一边，位于场外：每张[[养育场]]地点；奇丑混种和双面的带鳞寄生虫[tdc_rune_t]敌人；玛莉亚·里维拉、古代遗物[tdc_rune_s]和骇人“面具”剧情支援；<i>朝圣者</i>和<i>穷途异魔</i>遭遇组；以及每张寄生变形弱点。"

msgid "Set each of the following aside, out of play: each [[Apiary]] location, the Grotesque Amalgam, Mother, and double-sided Squamous Parasite [tdc_rune_t] enemies, the Grisly \"Mask\" and Ancient Relic [tdc_rune_s] story assets, and each copy of the Parasitic Transformation weakness."
msgstr "将以下卡牌放在一边，位于场外：每张[[养育场]]地点；奇丑混种、主母和双面的带鳞寄生虫[tdc_rune_t]敌人；古代遗物[tdc_rune_s]和骇人“面具”剧情支援；以及每张寄生变形弱点。"

msgid "Check the campaign log. If <i>the creature was defeated:</i>"
msgstr "检查剧本日志。如果<i>那头怪物被击败了：</i>"

msgid "Also gather <i>The Inescapable</i> encounter set, and set it aside, out of play."
msgstr "将<i>穷途异魔</i>遭遇组从游戏中移除"

msgid "Shuffle each remaining encounter card to build the encounter deck along with the following set-aside [[Apiary]] locations: Growing Fields and both copies of Fleshy Paths."
msgstr "将剩余的每张遭遇卡牌连同放在一边的增生原野和每张血肉道路一起混洗，组成遭遇牌库。"

msgid "After doing so, shuffle the set-aside Luminous Tunnels location into the bottom 10 cards of the encounter deck."
msgstr "之后，再将放在一边的荧光通道地点混洗入遭遇牌库底的10张卡牌。"

msgid "After doing so, shuffle the set-aside Grasping Corridor location into the bottom 10 cards of the encounter deck."
msgstr "之后，再将放在一边的攫噬长廊地点混洗入遭遇牌库底的10张卡牌。"

msgid "Lost Pilgrims"
msgstr "失落的朝圣者"

msgid "Hive Mind"
msgstr "蜂巢思维"

msgid "Scenario Interlude: Lost Pilgrims"
msgstr "冒险幕间故事：失落的朝圣者"

msgid ""
"Coughing weakly, the woman introduces herself as Maria Rivera. She and the others are a collective of pilgrims from all walks of life, led to this place by their dreams. “This is the domain of the drowned god, the dead monarch Cthulhu. We have been instructed by our leader, Lady Dao, to await his return in this ancient city.” The name “Cthulhu” rings in your ears. You have heard it time and again in your dreams."
"Maria continues. “However, there is something malevolent living in these tunnels. Something I fear we awakened by our presence. We sent one of our own to find help, but they haven’t returned.”"
"Your discussion is cut short by a dreadful roar. Maria lowers her gaze. “Since we arrived, we’ve been pursued by something… something awful. It hunted us through the streets, the ancient archive, and even through the city’s heart. I hoped it would not follow us to this corrupt and horrible place.” She coughs weakly. “I do not have the strength to lead them out of these tunnels. Please, I beg you, lead us to safety.”"
"Another roar echoes through the tunnels, closer this time, accompanied by the trilling of parasites. Andy looks to you, then to Maria and says, “Gather your people. Nobody deserves to die down here.”"
msgstr ""
"带着虚弱的咳嗽，这个女子自我介绍说她叫玛莉亚·里维拉。她和这群朝圣者背景各不相同，都是受梦感召而来。“这里是溺亡之神，死去的主君克苏鲁的领域。我们受到领袖道夫人的指示来此，恭迎他返回古城。”“克苏鲁”这个名字在你耳畔响起。你在梦里一次次地听过这个名字。"
"玛莉亚继续道：“然而，这些隧道里有什么邪恶的东西，我怀疑是因为我们来此才唤醒的东西。我们派了个人去求援，但音讯全无。”"
"你们的对话被一声可怕的吼叫打断了。玛莉亚垂下眼睛：“我们一来，就被什么东西追赶……它很可怕。它追猎我们穿过街道、古代的档案馆，甚至是城市的心胜。我希望它别跟我们来这片腐败又可怕的地方。”她又虚弱地咳嗽了，“我确实没有力量带领他们穿越这些隧道了。拜托了，我恳求你，带我们去安全的地方吧。”"
"隧道里传来又一声吼叫，这次更近了，还夹杂着寄生虫的颤音。安迪看看你，又看向玛莉亚说：“带好你的人。谁都不该死在这里。”"

msgid "Flip Apiary Entrance to its <i>(Dangerous Exit)</i> side."
msgstr "将养育场入口翻至<i>（危险出口）</i>面。"

msgid "Search the encounter deck, discard pile, and all in- and out of play areas for each non-weakness [[Cultist]] enemy. Shuffle them together and place them in a facedown stack beneath Lost Campsite."
msgstr "查找遭遇牌库、遭遇弃牌堆和所有场上和场外区域，找出所有非弱点[[异数徒]]敌人。混洗他们，并正面朝下放作一堆，放在迷失营地底下。"

msgid "Choose an investigator to take control of the set aside Maria Rivera story asset. <i>(Remember that Maria is also a [[Cultist]] who can be saved!)</i>"
msgstr "选择一位调查员控制放在一边的玛莉亚·里维拉剧情支援。<i>（记住玛利亚也是要拯救的[[异数徒]]!）</i>"

msgid "Spawn the set-aside The Inescapable enemy, exhausted, at the location farthest from all investigators. Shuffle the rest of <i>The Inescapable</i> encounter set into the encounter deck, along with the encounter discard pile."
msgstr "将放在一边的穷途异魔敌人以横置状态生成在离所有调查员最远的地点。将<i>穷途异魔</i>遭遇组的剩余卡牌和遭遇弃牌堆一起混洗入遭遇牌库。"

msgid "Place clues on each revealed location without <b>victory X</b> up to its clue value."
msgstr "在每个没有<b>胜利X</b>的已揭示地点上放置线索，直至其线索等于其线索值。"

msgid "Scenario Interlude: Hive Mind"
msgstr "冒险幕间故事：蜂巢思维"

msgid ""
"You feel the rush of an alien consciousness as a thousand thoughts and memories encroach upon yours. She is your Mother. You feel it deep within. You see a legion of winged, tentacled monstrosities entering an otherworldly vessel. You see Mother, small as a worm, crawl out of her host. You see her enter another host, and then another, laying eggs within their gullets. You feel her need to grow, to spread, to proliferate. Then the taste of alien flesh, of human flesh, of your own flesh as Mother tastes you even now."
"You awaken to see Ruby standing over you, knife in hand. You are in a pulsing, fetid chamber, the cord that linked you to the Mother flails like a lizard’s tail on the ground before you. Embedded in the walls of the chamber is a massive corpse of an alien creature held up like a grisly puppet. Mother herself. You feel her desire to absorb you, to become you, to devour you."
"“We have to kill it,” Ruby growls."
msgstr ""
"异样的思维不断涌入，千百种思绪和记忆蚕食着你的脑海。她是你的主母。你深深地意识到了。你看到有翼的触手怪大军正进入外星的血管。你看到主母小如蠕虫，正从宿主体内爬出。你看到她进入另一个宿主体内，之后又一个，在他们的食道里产卵。你感到她需要生长、扩散、繁衍。然后是外星血肉的味道、人类血肉的味道、你自己血肉的味道，因为主母正在品尝的就是你。"
"你醒了，看到露比站在面前，手里拿着刀。你身处恶臭的活腔室中；连接你和主母的东西像蜥蜴的尾巴，就落在你面前的地上。腔室的墙里架着一具巨大的异星尸体，像可怕的木偶：那就是主母。你感受到她的愿望：吸收你、成为你、吞噬你。"
"“我们得杀了它。”露比吼道。"

msgid "Rearrange the Apiary Entrance, Grasping Corridor, Starving Corridor, and Acidic Coelom in a circle as shown in the location placement diagram to the right. Place each other location with <b>victory X</b> and no clues on it in the victory display, discarding all tokens and cards at those locations."
msgstr "按照右边的地点摆放示意图，重新摆放养育场入口、攫噬长廊、饥渴长廊、酸性体腔，使其围成一圈。将其他每个有<b>胜利X</b>且没有线索的地点放入胜利区，弃掉这些地点上所有的标记和卡牌。"

msgid "Act 2a - The Hive Mind"
msgstr "场景2a——蜂巢思维"

